data.description: Take advantage and enjoy the benefit to clean up and update this multi-family investment opportunity to obtain these two corner lot homes in Mammoth Arizona.  The homes are being sold together. The main house-103 S Verdugo Place has been updated with forced air and heating with updated window, which was built in 1954, at 1275-sf with 3 bedrooms, 1 bath with detached workshop.  The smaller house 110 E Copper Street was built in 1940 at 546-sf, with 2 bedrooms, 1 bath, plus a detached garage. You can live in the main house, rent them both or rent the smaller home or use as an ADU.  Parcel numbers include 306-17-054 & 306-17-053. You will have the workshop and garage with plenty of work space and storage for equipment, etc.
